00:00:58.690 --> 00:00:59.880 align:middle line:90%
And do you practice?

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:04.129 align:middle line:84%
What is your day to day life
like so that we can understand

00:01:04.129 --> 00:01:07.290 align:middle line:84%
how you came to this
place of teaching people

00:01:07.290 --> 00:01:10.450 align:middle line:84%
to live more fully and
more in the present moment?

00:01:10.450 --> 00:01:12.820 align:middle line:84%
I lecture at Leeds
Metropolitan University.

00:01:12.820 --> 00:01:15.750 align:middle line:84%
I'm I lecturer in
transversal psychology.

00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:18.980 align:middle line:84%
And ever since I
was a teenager--

00:01:18.980 --> 00:01:20.780 align:middle line:84%
maybe 15 or
16-years-old-- I've always

00:01:20.780 --> 00:01:25.280 align:middle line:84%
felt connected to something
spiritual inside myself.

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:27.790 align:middle line:84%
So when I was a teenager,
I was the complete opposite

00:01:27.790 --> 00:01:28.670 align:middle line:90%
of a normal teenager.

00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:30.390 align:middle line:90%
I didn't go out to nightclubs.

00:01:30.390 --> 00:01:32.820 align:middle line:84%
I went to open spaces
and fields and parks

00:01:32.820 --> 00:01:35.400 align:middle line:90%
to walk around on my own.

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.200 align:middle line:84%
And I felt very
attracted to nature,

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:41.740 align:middle line:90%
to stillness, and to quietness.

00:01:41.740 --> 00:01:44.220 align:middle line:84%
And, as a result, people
thought I was a bit strange.

00:01:44.220 --> 00:01:47.080 align:middle line:84%
And I thought I
was a bit strange.

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:49.790 align:middle line:84%
So it took me a
long time to accept

00:01:49.790 --> 00:01:52.260 align:middle line:84%
my basic spiritual nature
and to understand it

00:01:52.260 --> 00:01:54.150 align:middle line:84%
because my background
was completely

00:01:54.150 --> 00:01:57.140 align:middle line:84%
non-spiritual,
non-religious, typical kind

00:01:57.140 --> 00:01:59.900 align:middle line:84%
of northern working
class English background.

00:01:59.900 --> 00:02:01.910 align:middle line:84%
So it took me a long time to
understand myself completely.

00:02:01.910 --> 00:02:07.640 align:middle line:84%
But once I did, once I realized
that there was such a thing

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:09.060 align:middle line:84%
as meditation, and
there was such things

00:02:09.060 --> 00:02:11.650 align:middle line:84%
as spiritual traditions
and spiritual books,

00:02:11.650 --> 00:02:14.400 align:middle line:84%
they gave me a framework
to understand myself.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:21.020 align:middle line:84%
And after that I integrated
spirituality into my life.

00:02:21.020 --> 00:02:22.680 align:middle line:90%
And life is quite hectic now.

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:24.820 align:middle line:90%
I've three young children.

00:02:24.820 --> 00:02:26.900 align:middle line:90%
And so life is quite busy.

00:02:26.900 --> 00:02:28.080 align:middle line:90%
And I'm working as a lecturer.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:29.840 align:middle line:84%
I'm trying to write
whenever I can.

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:34.530 align:middle line:84%
The difficult thing is finding
time to do some writing.

00:02:34.530 --> 00:02:37.320 align:middle line:84%
It's quite impressive to have
even Eckhart Tolle say that you

00:02:37.320 --> 00:02:39.470 align:middle line:90%
bring an important piece here.

00:02:39.470 --> 00:02:41.520 align:middle line:84%
And Eckhart Tolle
obviously is right now

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:44.680 align:middle line:84%
I think the number one
I mean in that hundred

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:46.000 align:middle line:84%
top spiritual
people in the world.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:47.900 align:middle line:84%
You're part of that list, too.
-Yeah.

00:02:47.900 --> 00:02:50.380 align:middle line:84%
I think Eckhart has gone
down to number two now.

00:02:50.380 --> 00:02:53.870 align:middle line:90%
The Dali Lama is number one.

00:02:53.870 --> 00:02:55.490 align:middle line:90%
But I'm working my way up.

00:02:55.490 --> 00:02:58.131 align:middle line:84%
Next year I expect
to be in the top 10.

